# Env variables for docker-compose, on host, for generic wm installation scenarios

### Use this as a reference for all dependent projects as well
### WARNING: the _MOUNT_POINT variables are not to be changed in normal conditions

## Project Options
### folder inside the container for the runs logs 
H_WMLAB_RUN_BASE_MOUNT_POINT=/mnt/runs
### Take snapshots during installation, fixing, general setup: 0-off 1-on
H_WMLAB_TAKE_SNAPHOTS=0
### Debug messages in logs: 0-off 1-on
H_WMLAB_DEBUG_ON=1
H_WMLAB_ENTRY_POINT=/mnt/scripts/local/defaultEntryPoint.sh
### Install Home
H_WMLAB_INSTALL_HOME=/opt/sag/products
### SUM Install home
H_WMLAB_SUM_HOME=/opt/sag/sum

### Patch installation or not? 0 - yes, 1- not
H_WMLAB_SKIP_PATCHING=0
### Online or offline patching? 1 - online 0 - offline (will require fixes image)
H_WMLAB_FIXES_ONLINE=0

## Installation assets

### Local environment - change according to your environment
H_WMLAB_PRODUCTS_VERSION=1005

### Installation Assets Mount points - do not change
H_WMLAB_INSTALLER_BIN_MOUNT_POINT=/opt/sag/mnt/wm-install-files/installer.bin
H_WMLAB_PRODUCTS_IMAGE_MOUNT_POINT=/opt/sag/mnt/wm-install-files/products.zip

## Fixing assets
### Credentials for online patching (not used if patching occurs online)
H_WMLAB_FIXES_ONLINE_CRED_FILE=..\config\secret\empower-credentials-fixes.txt

#### Fixing assete mount points - do not change
H_WMLAB_SUM10_BOOTSTRAP_BIN_MOUNT_POINT=/opt/sag/mnt/wm-install-files/sum-v10-bootstrap.bin
H_WMLAB_SUM11_BOOTSTRAP_BIN_MOUNT_POINT=/opt/sag/mnt/wm-install-files/sum-v11-bootstrap.bin
H_WMLAB_FIXES_IMAGE_FILE_MOUNT_POINT=/opt/sag/mnt/wm-install-files/fixes.zip
H_WMLAB_FIXES_ONLINE_CRED_FILE_MOUNT_POINT=/mnt/secret/empower-credentials-fixes.txt

